Modifier	            Allowed in Interfaces?	    Since	    Notes
public	                ✅	                        Always	    All interface methods are implicitly public
default	                ✅	                        Java 8	    Must have body, used for backward compatibility
static	                ✅	                        Java 8	    Used for utility methods
private	                ✅	                        Java 9	    Helper method for use within interface only
private static	        ✅	                        Java 9	    For reusable logic in static methods
abstract private	    ❌	                           —	    Invalid combination